data.description: Experience the epitome of California living at this meticulously crafted single level luxury home that offers a perfect blend of elegance, comfort, and sophistication. Nestled in a coveted neighborhood at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac with a private gate, this stunning home boasts modern amenities and timeless architectural design.  Step inside to discover a spacious and inviting interior filled with natural light, accentuated by high ceilings and luxurious finishes. The open-concept living spaces flow seamlessly, creating an ideal setting for both entertaining and everyday living. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring premium appliances, granite countertops, maple cabinets, a six-burner stove, double ovens and a walk-in pantry with ample storage space.The master suite serves as a serene retreat, offering a peaceful ambiance and a spa-like ensuite bathroom complete with a soaking tub and a separate shower. The 4 additional bedrooms are generously sized, and 3 have en-suite bathrooms, providing comfort and privacy for family and guests.  The expansive low-maintenance backyard oasis awaits, offering a private sanctuary to relax and unwind on almost an acre. Enjoy evenings under the covered patio or two gazebos, at the fire pit or water feature, or on the large paver patio. There is also plenty of room for a large pool or ADU.   Conveniently located, Hamilton provides easy access to shopping, dining, recreational activities, and top-rated schools. This is more than just a home; it's a lifestyle opportunity that encapsulates the essence of Southern California living.
